FDA panelist: Force vaccine on your kids to see if it’s safe. He's not a nice guy! Mean Joe campaigns for McAuliffe. Georgia Governor Kemp talks election law, Braves in World Series. Future C&B guest host Michael Berry of NewsRadio 740 KTRH drops by to discuss the day's essential news.
